Package: cQL
Type: Package
Title: Clustered Q-Learning with the M-out-of-N Cluster Bootstrap
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yao", "Song", email = "yaos@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Author: Yao Song [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yao Song <yaos@umich.edu>
Description: Implements clustered Q-learning for two-stage clustered
    sequential multiple assignment randomized trials (cSMARTs) using the
    manuscript's M-out-of-N cluster bootstrap procedure. The package supports
    both full second-stage re-randomization (type I cSMARTs) and limited
    second-stage re-randomization (type II/III cSMARTs) by allowing the
    stage-2 treatment column to be missing for clusters that were not
    re-randomized.
